#: ../../../server-side-search/index.rst:81
msgid "Search as you type"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../server-side-search/index.rst:83
msgid ""
"Search as-you-type allows users to quickly find exactly what they are "
"looking for while typing. It also saves recent searches, for future "
"reference."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../server-side-search/index.rst:86
msgid "Try it by pressing :guilabel:`/` (forward slash) and typing."
